 ('123', '300', 'en_us', 'PARENTS NIGHT OUT', '<p>Date Night, Ladies Night, Netflix or Catch-Up-On-Sleep Night. Whatever your plans, bring the kiddos to FPMA.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We\'re hosting a Nerf themed Parents Night Out on&nbsp;Saturday, September 24th from 5-9pm. $50 per kid/$80 for two. Grab your Nerf Blaster, ammo and bring a friend (non-FPMA students welcome) and join for a night full of pizza, movies, and ammo!</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'location', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2016-09-19 03:42:48', '2016-09-27 13:56:49', 'd3087dfc-696c-4780-8d6f-7f297647ea6a'),
 ('124', '314', 'en_us', 'NEW BREED ULTIMATE CHALLENGE   ', '<p>We are encouraging those that&nbsp;are competition ready to register for the New Breed Tournament. New Breed&nbsp;is open to all styles and skills level and the grand prize of $2,500!!&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Preregister online to by OCTOBER&nbsp;30th to receive discounted entry fee and free event tee. <a href=\"http://www.newbreedus.com\">www.newbreedus.com</a>&nbsp;New Breed Ultimate Challenge will be held at the&nbsp;Sportplex at Valley View, located at&nbsp;5702 Alpha Road Dallas,TX.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>For more details go online to&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.newbreedus.com/\">www.newbreedus.com</a> or ask any FPMA&nbsp;instructor!&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'location', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2016-09-27 14:15:05', '2016-11-15 15:37:18', '6045a6a1-e3d7-4178-aa36-db13869d1c25'),
 ('125', '335', 'en_us', 'HALLOWEEN PARTY + PARENTS NIGHT OUT ', '<p>Give the kids another chance to wear their costumes!&nbsp;Both Freddie Poole Martial Arts and North Texas Martial Arts are hosting a Halloween themed Parents Night Out.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Friday, October 21st from 5PM&nbsp;- 9PM&nbsp;at North Texas Martial Arts&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Saturday, October 29th from 5PM&nbsp;- 9PM&nbsp;at Freddie Poole Martial Arts&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Join&nbsp;us for a night full of pizza, movies, and prizes. As always, non-members are welcomed, so please bring a friend. Space is limited so please reach out to each location to reserve your spot!&nbsp;<br></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'location', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', '2016-10-13 03:32:23', '2016-11-01 14:27:05', 'a6ebfb82-baf5-41f0-a9f7-93a5001cdeaf'),
