 ('67', '17', '3', '1', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Juniors\",\"slug\":\"juniors\",\"postDate\":1458100080,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"6\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"secondaryHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Juniors: (7 to 12 years old) \",\"body\":\"<p>Freddie Poole\\u2019s Martial Arts\\u00ae&nbsp;junior martial arts program&nbsp;is a unique training system that combines traditional values and principles with a modern system of combat, self-defense and fitness. Our exclusive system and program is a hybrid style, which incorporates training methods of karate and tae-kwon-do with westernized boxing, judo and Brazilian Jiu Jitsu. FPMA has a variety of instructors teaching our program. This gives students an advantage of learning martial arts from different perspectives, which enhances the quality of training.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"mapTitle\":\"\",\"mapContent\":\"\",\"mapAddress\":\"\",\"flexibleArea\":\"\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"body\":\"<p>Our Juniors program focuses on advancement and growth based on each child\\u2019s individual pace. The key to our success is each discipline is introduced in stages to the student, rather than front-loading a program. Juniors will begin to grasp the concept of self-discipline as they achieve goals. When he\\/she tackles more difficult goals, the self-confidence grows and serves as a strong foundation in all aspects of life.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}}},\"22\":\"Juniors (7 -12 YO)\",\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-06-15 03:14:24', '2016-06-15 03:14:24', 'd34c5bfb-3ccb-4b47-84d4-39cae634e7c6'),
 ('68', '17', '3', '1', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Juniors\",\"slug\":\"juniors\",\"postDate\":1458100080,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"6\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"79\":{\"type\":\"secondaryHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Juniors: (7 to 12 years old) \",\"body\":\"<p>Freddie Poole\\u2019s Martial Arts\\u00ae&nbsp;junior martial arts program&nbsp;is a unique training system that combines traditional values and principles with a modern system of combat, self-defense and fitness. Our exclusive system and program is a hybrid style, which incorporates training methods of karate and tae-kwon-do with westernized boxing, judo and Brazilian Jiu Jitsu. FPMA has a variety of instructors teaching our program. This gives students an advantage of learning martial arts from different perspectives, which enhances the quality of training.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"8\"],\"mapTitle\":\"\",\"mapContent\":\"\",\"mapAddress\":\"\",\"flexibleArea\":\"\"}},\"80\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"body\":\"<p>Our Juniors program focuses on advancement and growth based on each child\\u2019s individual pace. The key to our success is each discipline is introduced in stages to the student, rather than front-loading a program. Juniors will begin to grasp the concept of self-discipline as they achieve goals. When he\\/she tackles more difficult goals, the self-confidence grows and serves as a strong foundation in all aspects of life.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}}},\"22\":\"Juniors (7 -12 YO)\",\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-06-15 03:14:59', '2016-06-15 03:14:59', 'bd56e40c-3d56-4aff-9c84-52999891c654'),
 ('69', '81', '3', '1', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu\",\"slug\":\"brazilian-jiu-jitsu\",\"postDate\":1465960807,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"secondaryHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu: (7 to 12-year-old + Adults) \",\"body\":\"<p>The sport of Brazilian Jiu Jitsu can be quite complex. Our intro program helps break down all the essential concepts of the sport making it much easier to pick up for anybody. Freddie Poole\\u2019s Martial arts is a proud affiliate of the Carlos Machado BJJ association and network. Carlos Machado is nephew to one of the founders of Brazilian Jiu Jitsu, late master Carlos Gracie. Carlos is determined to keep the legacy going through teaching and partnering with others including our very own, Freddie Poole.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"mapTitle\":\"\",\"mapContent\":\"\",\"mapAddress\":\"\",\"flexibleArea\":\"\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"body\":\"<p>Our classes are curriculum oriented, providing a fast paced yet easy approach to learning Brazilian Jiu Jitsu for children (7-12 years of age) and adults. Students achieve great results in a short amount of time learning realistic skills great for both self-defense and increasing fitness and stamina. Students also learn strategies for advancing in rank after completing time and skill requirements, all in a fun and safe environment.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}},\"new4\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Kids BJJ Program\",\"body\":\"<p>The FPMA Brazilian Jiu Jitsu kids program is the perfect tool to change your child\\u2019s life forever. Lessons learned both on and off the mat will instill in them a confidence and self-belief that will continue with them throughout their lives. Plus, it\\u2019s FUN! FPMA stands firm on our anti-bullying policies, which have been reverse engineered to safely and effectively repel any aggressor, with truly phenomenal results.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Overall, the Kids BBJ program is designed to develop a sense of discipline, determination, leadership, commitment, responsibility, good sportsmanship and confidence into our future leaders<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f5f5f5\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}},\"new5\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Adults BJJ Fundamentals\",\"body\":\"<p>FPMA BJJ Fundamentals Program is designed to teach the overall self-defense strategy of Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu. The class begins with a pre-workout involving many body weight exercises and it will teach you the basics, from learning how to fall, to clinching, taking down and successfully setting up and applying a submission hold as well as various escapes. We provide a detailed instruction in wrestling, judo, and Brazilian Jiu Jitsu, as they are all relevant to mastership. The class ends with positional training that helps students focus on the lesson of the week and get a feel for live training. Through repetition techniques, your training will slowly prepare you to begin drilling at a full resistance.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}}},\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-06-15 03:20:08', '2016-06-15 03:20:08', 'ea1b86a8-5dfb-4a95-b325-05859a6c49e2'),
 ('70', '81', '3', '1', 'en_us', '2', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu\",\"slug\":\"brazilian-jiu-jitsu\",\"postDate\":1465960800,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"82\":{\"type\":\"secondaryHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu\",\"body\":\"<p>The sport of Brazilian Jiu Jitsu can be quite complex. Our intro program helps break down all the essential concepts of the sport making it much easier to pick up for anybody. Freddie Poole\\u2019s Martial arts is a proud affiliate of the Carlos Machado BJJ association and network. Carlos Machado is nephew to one of the founders of Brazilian Jiu Jitsu, late master Carlos Gracie. Carlos is determined to keep the legacy going through teaching and partnering with others including our very own, Freddie Poole.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\",\"mapTitle\":\"\",\"mapContent\":\"\",\"mapAddress\":\"\",\"flexibleArea\":\"\"}},\"83\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"body\":\"<p>Our classes are curriculum oriented, providing a fast paced yet easy approach to learning Brazilian Jiu Jitsu for children (7-12 years of age) and adults. Students achieve great results in a short amount of time learning realistic skills great for both self-defense and increasing fitness and stamina. Students also learn strategies for advancing in rank after completing time and skill requirements, all in a fun and safe environment.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}},\"84\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Kids BJJ Program\",\"body\":\"<p>The FPMA Brazilian Jiu Jitsu kids program is the perfect tool to change your child\\u2019s life forever. Lessons learned both on and off the mat will instill in them a confidence and self-belief that will continue with them throughout their lives. Plus, it\\u2019s FUN! FPMA stands firm on our anti-bullying policies, which have been reverse engineered to safely and effectively repel any aggressor, with truly phenomenal results.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Overall, the Kids BBJ program is designed to develop a sense of discipline, determination, leadership, commitment, responsibility, good sportsmanship and confidence into our future leaders<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f5f5f5\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}},\"85\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Adults BJJ Fundamentals\",\"body\":\"<p>FPMA BJJ Fundamentals Program is designed to teach the overall self-defense strategy of Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu. The class begins with a pre-workout involving many body weight exercises and it will teach you the basics, from learning how to fall, to clinching, taking down and successfully setting up and applying a submission hold as well as various escapes. We provide a detailed instruction in wrestling, judo, and Brazilian Jiu Jitsu, as they are all relevant to mastership. The class ends with positional training that helps students focus on the lesson of the week and get a feel for live training. Through repetition techniques, your training will slowly prepare you to begin drilling at a full resistance.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}}},\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-06-15 03:20:32', '2016-06-15 03:20:32', 'ed6066e7-88c5-4ff3-a8ec-c6859cb0acae'),
 ('71', '86', '3', '1', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Ladies Kickboxing\",\"slug\":\"ladies-kickboxing\",\"postDate\":1465960944,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Ladies Kickboxing\",\"body\":\"<p>The Ladies Kickboxing program is exclusively for ladies looking to combine an intense physical workout with the added perk of self-defense practices. Outside of incorporating various types of kickboxing techniques and strikes, FPMA Ladies kickboxing helps to educate students on many aspects of weight training, physical conditioning and yoga.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"8\"]}},\"new3\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"body\":\"<p>As intimidating as it may sound, kickboxing is perfect for all ladies. From beginners to experts, you\\u2019re sure to get the most from the&nbsp;private like atmosphere and pace of the class. With a dedicated staff of skilled professionals, kickboxing is the ideal workout option for mothers looking for an alternative to going to the gym and unique workout options with morning, afternoon and evening classes available.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}}},\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-06-15 03:22:24', '2016-06-15 03:22:24', '3ae32c11-0850-432c-934f-0bc4f695ceb2'),
 ('72', '89', '3', '1', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Martial Arts\",\"slug\":\"martial-arts\",\"postDate\":1465961192,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"secondaryHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Martial Arts\",\"body\":\"<p><strong>Martial Arts (7 to 12 years old + Adults)<\\/strong><\\/p><p>Martial arts training helps to develop an indomitable spirit in practitioners of any age and any skill level. FPMA martial arts program focuses on increased concentration, ability to memorize and awareness. Many of our students say there is no better stress relief than coming onto the mat and pushing their minds, bodies and spirits to the limits.<\\/p>\",\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"8\"],\"mapTitle\":\"\",\"mapContent\":\"\",\"mapAddress\":\"\",\"flexibleArea\":\"\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Martial Arts: Juniors\",\"body\":\"<h3>Freddie Poole Beginner\\u2019s Course (White Belts):<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>This class begins with traditional Chung Do Kwon (Tae Kwon Do) and karate. Students learn basic commands, basic stances and blocks, and basic kicks and punches. This program implements boxing to enhance and modernize the system. Students\\u2019 progress through short-term goals (stripes) to reach their long-term goal (colored rank). Students learn practical and situational self-defense as well. Classes are thirty minutes (for greater retention of material), in a fun, yet disciplined and true martial arts environment.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3>Freddie Poole Intermediate Course (Orange through Purple belts):<\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The Freddie Poole Intermediate Karate Course focuses on the student\\u2019s concentration and increases physical fitness through agility and coordination drills. Balance and kicking technique are emphasized as well as an introduction to sparring technique and strategy. Each step of the way, children are guided towards a true understanding of their new found skills and associated responsibilities. To balance and complete the intermediate program, students will learn basic judo and take downs (blue belt). Class time will increase to 45 minutes to an hour long.<\\/p><h3>Freddie Poole Advanced Course (Red through Black Belt):<\\/h3><p>In the Freddie Poole Advanced Karate Program, students are introduced to advanced technique drills and advanced forms. Students\\u2019 progress to a more intense and advanced sparring level in preparation for Black Belt. To create a well-balanced program and student, the Freddie Poole Advanced course focuses on self-defense and mental awareness, with a heavy emphasis on grappling and Brazilian Jiu Jitsu fitness goals.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}},\"new3\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Martial Arts: Adults\",\"body\":\"<p>The adult curriculum is a structured traditional program complimented by modern training techniques that provide students the opportunity to understand theory as well as practical application.<\\/p><p>Students learn techniques and strategies that can truly be life-saving skills as well as give overall fitness. New students will see improvement in their coordination, flexibility and muscle tone in just a few short weeks. Those who become proficient in martial arts will have better stamina, strength and peace of mind that comes from knowing they can efficiently and effectively defend themselves.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f5f5f5\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}}},\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-06-15 03:26:32', '2016-06-15 03:26:32', 'd720dc9a-10b9-4594-a91f-048962eef0d6'),
 ('73', '93', '3', '1', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Muay Thai\",\"slug\":\"muay-thai\",\"postDate\":1465961434,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"secondaryHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Muay Thai: Adults\",\"body\":\"<p>Muay Thai is a combat sport from Thailand that uses stand-up strikes along with various clinch techniques. This physical and mental discipline is known as \\\"the art of eight limbs\\\" because it is characterized by the combined use of fists, elbows, knees and shins during training.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"40\"],\"mapTitle\":\"\",\"mapContent\":\"\",\"mapAddress\":\"\",\"flexibleArea\":\"\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"body\":\"<p>Individuals participating in this program achieve outstanding physical conditioning due to the highly intense yet fun&nbsp;nature of striking through the use of bag&nbsp;drills, mitt drills&nbsp;and pad work. This self paced class is taught by high level instructors with years of training in this discipline, who encourage each participant to reach their full physical potential. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}}},\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-06-15 03:30:34', '2016-06-15 03:30:34', '319ba553-44bf-4597-93f9-b426b7bcb999'),
 ('74', '96', '3', '1', 'en_us', '1', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Leadership\",\"slug\":\"leadership\",\"postDate\":1465961494,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"new1\":{\"type\":\"secondaryHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Leadership\",\"body\":\"<p>The FPMA Leadership Program is an instructor recommended program. Students must first attain a blue belt through the Intermediate Program. They must also demonstrate leadership qualities to receive nominations.<\\/p>\",\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"8\"],\"mapTitle\":\"\",\"mapContent\":\"\",\"mapAddress\":\"\",\"flexibleArea\":\"\"}},\"new2\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"body\":\"<p>The FPMA Leadership Program focuses on developing leaders, not only in Martial Arts, but in the community as well. Each month leadership students are required to demonstrate and apply a new leadership skill at home, at school, and in the Martial&nbsp;Arts training.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}}},\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-06-15 03:31:34', '2016-06-15 03:31:34', '0090fcf7-29e7-4304-a4a8-499244a2577e'),
 ('75', '27', '3', '1', 'en_us', '6', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Staff\",\"slug\":\"staff\",\"postDate\":1458873960,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"5\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"28\":{\"type\":\"secondaryHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Staff\",\"body\":\"<p>Our instructors have spent many years perfecting the martial arts craft and continue to go through extensive testing training and certifications to ensure that we are able to provide our students with the best care and instruction. <\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Here, we\\u2019re family and we truly enjoy what we do and we enjoy sharing that passion with others. Collectively we invest in each student, as we feel that their success is our success!&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"41\"],\"mapTitle\":\"\",\"mapContent\":\"\",\"mapAddress\":\"\",\"flexibleArea\":\"\"}},\"29\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"64\"],\"staffName\":\"Steve Sosa\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 7th degree black belt\",\"body\":\"<p>Master Steve Sosa has been an unstoppable, highly skilled martial artist for over 30 years. Master Sosa a 7th degree black belt in karate, trained by legendary martial artists such as Tim Kirby, Allen Steen, Ray McCallum, Billye Jackson, and Demetrius \\u201cThe Greek\\u201d Havanas - the original members of \\u201cTexas Blood \\u2018n\\u2019 Guts\\u201d karate in the Dallas area.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Master Sosa is a passionate trainer who has amassed several prestigious accolades in Martial Arts tournaments including \\u201cThe Golden Greek\\u201d which is the highest award given by the Amateur Organization of Karate. Master Sosa was also honored with the Positive Coaching Alliance\\u2019s Double-Goal Coaching Award, awarded to coaches who implement positive life skills, work ethic and drive into their students training.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>In 2010 Master Sosa started North Texas Martial Arts (NTMA), which ultimately joined Freddie Poole Martial Arts in 2015.<\\/p>\"}},\"30\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"62\"],\"staffName\":\"Jayda Clayton\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 2nd degree black belt\",\"body\":\"<p>Jayda Clayton, a 2nd degree black belt, began her training in January 2007 at the ripe old age of 4. A prodigy of Master Steven Sosa, Jayda received her yellow and brown belts in 2007 and 2009, respectively. At age 7, Jayda became Master Sosa\\u2019s first and youngest student to receive her black belt. Jayda has competed in numerous local, state and national karate competitions and won over 60 trophies in sparring and kata competitions with over 40 of them being first place positions.<\\/p>\"}},\"31\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"44\"],\"staffName\":\"Westin Poole\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 3rd degree black belt\",\"body\":\"<p>Westin Poole\\u2019s love for karate kicked in as a kid when began training in martial arts at the age of 6. By 2009, Westin was a certified 1st degree black belt and has no plans of slowing down. He has been teaching for almost eight years and enjoys working with children. The mission behind his teaching is inspiring his students to reach their goals and see the benefits of their hard work.&nbsp;<\\/p>\"}},\"65\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"99\"],\"staffName\":\"Vanny Boon\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 5th degree black belt, Saekson Muay Thai \",\"body\":\"<p>Master Vanny Boon is a certified 5th degree black belt skilled in various forms of martial arts including Taekwondo Do, Muay Thai, Brazilian Jiu jitsu and Boxing. Master Boon\\u2019s passion and experience for martial arts began when he started training at the age of 5 and spans over 25 years; Master Boon trained under Grand Master Hong, Master Freddie Poole and Muay Thai world champion Saekson Janjira.<\\/p>\"}},\"66\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"48\"],\"staffName\":\"Johnny Rodriguez\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, Machado black belt\",\"body\":\"<p>Professor Johnny Rodriguez is a highly skilled black belt in Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu with over 20 years of training in several martial art forms including Kenpo karate, Aikido, Judo and Muay Thai. Professor Rodriguez teaches workshops, self-defense seminars, and has previously worked in law enforcement. &nbsp;Professor Rodriguez actively coaches students in preparation for BJJ tournaments and MMA bouts and still competes in many Brazilian jiu-jitsu tournaments.&nbsp;<\\/p>\"}},\"67\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"49\"],\"staffName\":\"Gerardo Mulas\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, Certified Personal Trainer, Yoga\",\"body\":\"<p>Gerardo Mulas is a certified personal trainer, yoga and martial arts expert whose mission is educating students the benefits of fitness and health and wellness goals. Gerardo specializes in sports performance, weight loss, injury rehabilitation, stress relief, nutritional counseling and meal planning. Gerardo has over two decades of professional and collegiate athletics under his belt, along with extensive training in kickboxing, boxing and grappling.<\\/p>\"}},\"68\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"50\"],\"staffName\":\"Randy Stem\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 5th degree black belt, fitness trainer \",\"body\":\"<p>Randy Stem is a 5th degree black belt trained in Karate, Kickboxing, and Judo and currently in Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu. Randy studied under the teachings of Allen Steen, widely recognized as the \'Father of American Taekwondo\', and has over 45 years of experience mastering martial arts. Randy strongly encourages his students to build a firm foundation in martial arts early on by focusing on the development of basic fundamental motor skills and concepts.<\\/p>\"}},\"69\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"43\"],\"staffName\":\"Sovandy Om\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 5th degree black belt\",\"body\":\"<p>Master Sovandy Om is a 5th degree black belt, kickboxing fitness certified trainer and a FPMA student favorite. Master Om has trained extensively in Tae Kwon Do, MMA, Gymnastic, as well as Crossfit. Along with a passion for martial arts, Master Om has an even bigger passion for fitness. Master Om works tirelessly with helping the students execute proper technique to achieve the maximum benefits, as well as helping students reach and exceed their fitness goals.<\\/p>\"}},\"70\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"46\"],\"staffName\":\"Alex Garcia\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 2nd degree black belt\",\"body\":\"<p>Alex Garcia is a 2nd degree black belt in Tae Kwon Do who gravitated towards the world of martial arts at the age of 4. Alex soon began training to develop and perfect his skills for martial arts and became a student at Freddie Poole\'s Martial Arts at the age of 10. Within 2 years, Alex\\u2019s dedication transformed him into an avid competitor, in which Alex received several 1st place wins in state martial arts championships.<\\/p>\"}},\"71\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"45\"],\"staffName\":\"Nathan Bagby\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 3rd degree black belt, Muay Thai \",\"body\":\"<p>Nathanael \\u201cNathan\\u201d Bagby is a 3rd degree black belt and an accomplished Muay Thai fighter and instructor. Nathan first became interested and started training in martial arts at the age of 8, and in the past 25 years, has trained in Isshinryu Karate, Eskrima, Tae Kwon Do, American Kickboxing, Brazilian Jiu Jitsu, Close Quarter Combat, Boxing, and Muay Thai. &nbsp;Nathan has gone on to compete in several amateur and professional kickboxing and Muay Thai bouts.&nbsp;<\\/p>\"}},\"72\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"100\"],\"staffName\":\"Mike Rose\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, Machado black belt \",\"body\":\"<p>Mike Rose has over 25 years of martial arts training, competition, and teaching experience in both Judo and Brazilian Jiu Jitsu. Mike started training in Judo in 1992, when he received his black belt. In 1998, under the teachings of Greg Nelson, Mike began training in Brazilian Jiu Jitsu and received his blue belt in 1999 and his black belt in 2009.<\\/p>\"}}},\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-06-15 03:36:12', '2016-06-15 03:36:12', 'c511b40c-a76d-4c72-86ac-e54627290f39'),
 ('76', '2', '1', '1', 'en_us', '16', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Home\",\"slug\":\"homepage\",\"postDate\":1457804906,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"15\":{\"type\":\"homeHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Kick. Punch. Learn.\",\"body\":\"<p>Freddie Poole\\u2019s Martial Arts \\u00ae offers an exclusive hybrid training system that incorporates the traditional training values and principles of karate and tae-kwon-do with a contemporary system of combat, self-defense and fitness.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"10\"],\"contactButton\":\"1\"}},\"18\":{\"type\":\"homePrograms\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Approach\",\"body\":\"<p>The key to our success is each discipline being introduced in stages to our student, rather than a front-loading program. This methodical approach ensures students are learning and mastering techniques at the highest level, as opposed to just going through motions. Additionally, we have a variety of skilled instructors teaching our programs. This gives students an advantage of learning martial arts from varied perspectives, which enhances the quality of the training. Each instructor at FPMA\\u00ae is trained to recognize a student\\u2019s personality, learning style, and individual needs.<\\/p>\",\"programs\":[\"16\",\"17\",\"81\",\"86\",\"89\",\"93\",\"96\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"61\"]}},\"52\":{\"type\":\"homeLocations\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Locations\",\"body\":\"<p>We currently have 2 locations to serve you.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"11\"]}},\"53\":{\"type\":\"twoColumns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"bodyLeft\":\"<p>Come see for yourself why our martial arts system has been so popular for so many years. Our black belt instructors are here to help you achieve all your marital art and fitness goals.<\\/p>\",\"bodyRight\":\"\",\"c