 instill in them a confidence and self-belief that will continue with them throughout their lives. Plus, it\\u2019s FUN! FPMA stands firm on our anti-bullying policies, which have been reverse engineered to safely and effectively repel any aggressor, with truly phenomenal results.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Overall, the Kids BBJ program is designed to develop a sense of discipline, determination, leadership, commitment, responsibility, good sportsmanship and confidence into our future leaders<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f5f5f5\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}},\"85\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Adults BJJ Fundamentals\",\"body\":\"<p>FPMA BJJ Fundamentals Program is designed to teach the overall self-defense strategy of Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu. The class begins with a pre-workout involving many body weight exercises and it will teach you the basics, from learning how to fall, to clinching, taking down and successfully setting up and applying a submission hold as well as various escapes. We provide a detailed instruction in wrestling, judo, and Brazilian Jiu Jitsu, as they are all relevant to mastership. The class ends with positional training that helps students focus on the lesson of the week and get a feel for live training. Through repetition techniques, your training will slowly prepare you to begin drilling at a full resistance.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}}},\"22\":\"Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu\",\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-06-27 01:20:02', '2016-06-27 01:20:02', 'c4f6cb7d-d4da-469c-a717-11acd8b4ba0d'),
 ('101', '86', '3', '1', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Ladies Kickboxing\",\"slug\":\"ladies-kickboxing\",\"postDate\":1465960920,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"6\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"87\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Ladies Kickboxing\",\"body\":\"<p>The Ladies Kickboxing program is exclusively for ladies looking to combine an intense physical workout with the added perk of self-defense practices. Outside of incorporating various types of kickboxing techniques and strikes, FPMA Ladies kickboxing helps to educate students on many aspects of weight training, physical conditioning and yoga.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"8\"]}},\"88\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"body\":\"<p>As intimidating as it may sound, kickboxing is perfect for all ladies. From beginners to experts, you\\u2019re sure to get the most from the&nbsp;private like atmosphere and pace of the class. With a dedicated staff of skilled professionals, kickboxing is the ideal workout option for mothers looking for an alternative to going to the gym and unique workout options with morning, afternoon and evening classes available.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"12\"]}}},\"22\":\"Ladies Kickboxing\",\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-06-27 01:21:51', '2016-06-27 01:21:51', 'f3384a6b-80fa-4116-831b-1011aa33ca21'),
