 ('135', '33', '3', '1', 'en_us', '11', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Events\",\"slug\":\"events\",\"postDate\":1458879720,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"55\":{\"type\":\"secondaryHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Events\",\"body\":\"<p>We pride ourselves in offering superior service and training for parents and kids. Outside of our extensive martial arts programs offered at both of our Dallas locations, FPMA offers various extra personal services that are very educational, affordable and definitely FUN! From private birthday celebrations to women\\u2019s self-defense classes, there\\u2019s a special FPMA Extra for everyone.<\\/p>\",\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"39\"],\"mapTitle\":\"\",\"mapContent\":\"\",\"mapAddress\":\"\",\"flexibleArea\":\"\"}},\"56\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Parent\\u2019s Nights Out\",\"body\":\"<p>Got a date night or hang out with the crew night planned and need somewhere to take the kiddos? Bring \\u2018em to FPMA for Parents Night Out (PNO). The PNO program is on specified Saturdays from 5-9pm and welcomes both FPMA students and non-members to join in on a night full of pizza, movies, prizes and fun. <strong><em>Oh, did we mention Nerf gun wars, too?<\\/em><\\/strong> <a href=\\\"\\/locations#entry:7:url\\\">Just give one of our locations a call<\\/a> for more information, pricing and dates for the next PNO.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"12\"]}},\"57\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Birthday Parties\",\"body\":\"<p>Celebrate the birthday for your little martial artists Freddie Poole style! FPMA offers a personal experience with one of our many skilled instructors, ready to teach all of the little partiers some exciting new martial arts moves and put a unique spin on a birthday celebrations. Decorations, music and food are welcome. Interested in having your kid\\u2019s next birthday celebration at FPMA? <a href=\\\"tel:2143525425\\\">Give one of our locations a call<\\/a> for more information.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f5f5f5\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}},\"58\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Special Events\",\"body\":\"<p><strong>FPMA is proud to announce our summer 2016 Karate Camp for kids.<\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Karate Camp is designed for children ages 4-11 and provides the perfect summer getaway for kids interested in learning more about the many forms of martial art. Give you kids the opportunity to learn more about boosting leadership and teamwork skills, building and improving self confidence, self defense techniques, bully awareness as well as fun martial arts games and drills. Choose from 2 summer camp sessions only a $25 deposit required to reserve a spot. Reach out to a FPMA location for more details.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}},\"77\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Women\\u2019s Self Defense Seminars\",\"body\":\"<p>Safety for our members is a major priority for us. FPMA offers self-defense classes for women to learn how to protect themselves and their loved ones from unexpected attacks. Join FPMA for one of our Women\\u2019s Self Defense Seminars in partnership with Not Dead Yet Apparel. Come get hands-on training as we demonstrate various self-defense techniques, learn empowering safety awareness and practices. Attendance is always free, but we accept donations of $25 or more to benefit a designated local non-profit organization. Take the first step by contacting one of our locations for more information.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f5f5f5\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}},\"78\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Personal Training \",\"body\":\"<p>For the member who wants to learn the valuable techniques of martial arts outside of a group setting, FPMA offers specialized one-on-one training sessions. Members get individually structured personal instruction from one of our certified martial arts trainers. Training sessions are customized to benefit each student in any skill level, from a novice student wanting a more personal experience or an advanced student preparing for competition. <a href=\\\"\\/contact-us#entry:32:url\\\">Contact one of our two Dallas locations<\\/a> for more details.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":\"\"}}},\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-07-11 01:34:32', '2016-07-11 01:34:32', '51258501-8d15-4e3b-9baf-3d4c8bdabc2f'),
 ('136', '93', '3', '1', 'en_us', '5', '', '{\"typeId\":\"4\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Muay Thai Kickboxing\",\"slug\":\"muay-thai-kickboxing\",\"postDate\":1465961400,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"6\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"94\":{\"type\":\"secondaryHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Muay Thai Kickboxing\",\"body\":\"<p><strong>Muay Thai: Adults<\\/strong><br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Muay Thai is a combat sport from Thailand that uses stand-up strikes along with various clinch techniques. This physical and mental discipline is known as \\\"the art of eight limbs\\\" because it is characterized by the combined use of fists, elbows, knees and shins during training.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"40\"],\"mapTitle\":\"\",\"mapContent\":\"\",\"mapAddress\":\"\",\"flexibleArea\":\"\"}},\"95\":{\"type\":\"oneColumn\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"body\":\"<p>Individuals participating in this program achieve outstanding physical conditioning due to the highly intense yet fun&nbsp;nature of striking through the use of bag&nbsp;drills, mitt drills&nbsp;and pad work. This self paced class is taught by high level instructors with years of training in this discipline, who encourage each participant to reach their full physical potential. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"12\"]}}},\"22\":\"Muay Thai: Adults\",\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-07-11 01:34:49', '2016-07-11 01:34:49', '107de3ad-df9c-48aa-9c54-bdbd37db8417'),
