 ('373', '2', '1', '1', 'en_us', '23', '', '{\"typeId\":null,\"authorId\":null,\"title\":\"Home\",\"slug\":\"homepage\",\"postDate\":1457804906,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":null,\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"15\":{\"type\":\"homeHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Kick. Punch. Learn.\",\"body\":\"<p>Freddie Poole\\u2019s Martial Arts\\u00ae offers an exclusive hybrid training system that incorporates the traditional training values and principles of karate and tae-kwon-do with a contemporary system of combat, self-defense and fitness.<\\/p>\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"39\"],\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"slides\":[\"125\",\"126\",\"127\",\"300\"]}},\"18\":{\"type\":\"homePrograms\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Approach\",\"body\":\"<p>The key to our success is each discipline being introduced in stages to our student, rather than a front-loading program. This methodical approach ensures students are learning and mastering techniques at the highest level, as opposed to just going through motions. Additionally, we have a variety of skilled instructors teaching our programs. This gives students an advantage of learning martial arts from varied perspectives, which enhances the quality of the training. Each instructor at FPMA\\u00ae is trained to recognize a student\\u2019s personality, learning style, and individual needs.<\\/p>\",\"programs\":[\"16\",\"17\",\"81\",\"86\",\"89\",\"93\",\"96\"],\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"102\"]}},\"52\":{\"type\":\"homeLocations\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Locations\",\"body\":\"<p>We currently have 2 locations to serve you.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"101\"]}},\"53\":{\"type\":\"twoColumns\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"\",\"bodyLeft\":\"<p>Come see for yourself why our martial arts system has been so popular for so many years. Our black belt instructors are here to help you achieve all your marital art and fitness goals.<\\/p>\",\"bodyRight\":\"\",\"columnsLeft\":\"col-3-of-5\",\"columnsRight\":\"col-2-of-5\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"9\"],\"contactButton\":\"1\"}}}}}', '2016-09-20 18:33:25', '2016-09-20 18:33:25', '577168b4-ffa2-43f0-8c0c-7505b1231116'),
 ('374', '27', '3', '177', 'en_us', '14', '', '{\"typeId\":\"3\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Instructors\",\"slug\":\"instructors\",\"postDate\":1458873960,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"parentId\":\"5\",\"fields\":{\"5\":{\"28\":{\"type\":\"secondaryHero\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"heading\":\"Instructors\",\"body\":\"<p>Our instructors have spent many years perfecting the martial arts craft and continue to go through extensive testing training and certifications to ensure that we are able to provide our students with the best care and instruction. <\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Here, we\\u2019re family, and we&nbsp;enjoy what we do and enjoy sharing that passion with others. Collectively we invest in each student, as we feel that their success is our success!<\\/p>\",\"contactButton\":\"1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#000000\",\"backgroundImage\":[\"41\"],\"mapTitle\":\"\",\"mapContent\":\"\",\"mapAddress\":\"\",\"flexibleArea\":\"\"}},\"29\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"64\"],\"staffName\":\"Steve Sosa\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 7th degree black belt\",\"body\":\"<p>Master Steve Sosa has been an unstoppable, highly skilled martial artist for over 30 years. Master Sosa, a 8th degree black belt in karate, was&nbsp;trained by legendary martial artists such as Tim Kirby, Allen Steen, Ray McCallum, Billye Jackson, and Demetrius \\u201cThe Greek\\u201d Havanas - the original members of \\u201cTexas Blood \\u2018n\\u2019 Guts\\u201d karate in the Dallas area.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Master Sosa is a passionate trainer who has amassed several prestigious accolades in Martial Arts tournaments including \\u201cThe Golden Greek\\u201d which is the highest award given by the Amateur Organization of Karate. Master Sosa was also honored with the Positive Coaching Alliance\\u2019s Double-Goal Coaching Award, awarded to coaches who implement positive life skills, work ethic and drive into their students training.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>In 2010 Master Sosa started North Texas Martial Arts (NTMA), which ultimately joined Freddie Poole Martial Arts in 2015.<\\/p>\"}},\"65\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"99\"],\"staffName\":\"Vanny Boon\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 5th degree black belt, Saekson Muay Thai \",\"body\":\"<p>Master Vanny Boon is a certified 5th degree black belt skilled in various forms of martial arts including Taekwondo Do, Muay Thai, Brazilian Jiu jitsu and Boxing. Master Boon\\u2019s passion and experience for martial arts began when he started training at the age of 5 and spans over 25 years.&nbsp;Master Boon trained under Grand Master Hong, Master Freddie Poole and Muay Thai world champion Saekson Janjira.<\\/p>\"}},\"68\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"50\"],\"staffName\":\"Randy Stem\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 5th degree black belt, fitness trainer \",\"body\":\"<p>Randy Stem is a 5th degree black belt trained in Karate, Kickboxing, and Judo and Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu. Randy studied under the teachings of Allen Steen, widely recognized as the \'Father of American Taekwondo\', and has over 45 years of experience mastering martial arts. Randy strongly encourages his students to build a firm foundation in martial arts early on by focusing on the development of basic fundamental motor skills and concepts.<\\/p>\"}},\"31\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"44\"],\"staffName\":\"Westin Poole\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 3rd degree black belt\",\"body\":\"<p>Westin Poole\\u2019s love for karate kicked in as a kid when he&nbsp;began training in martial arts at the age of 6. By 2009, Westin was a certified 1st degree black belt and has no plans of slowing down. He has been teaching for almost eight years and enjoys working with children. The mission behind his teaching is inspiring his students to reach their goals and see the benefits of their hard work.&nbsp;<\\/p>\"}},\"70\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"46\"],\"staffName\":\"Alex Garcia\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 2nd degree black belt\",\"body\":\"<p>Alex Garcia is a 2nd degree black belt in Tae Kwon Do who gravitated towards the world of martial arts at the age of 4. Alex soon began training to develop and perfect his skills for martial arts and became a student at Freddie Poole\'s Martial Arts at the age of 10. Within 2 years, Alex\\u2019s dedication transformed him into an avid competitor.&nbsp;Alex received several 1st place wins in state martial arts championships.<\\/p>\"}},\"72\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"100\"],\"staffName\":\"Mike Rose\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, Machado black belt \",\"body\":\"<p>Mike Rose has over 25 years of martial arts training, competition, and teaching experience in both Judo and Brazilian Jiu Jitsu. Mike started training in Judo in 1992 and currently&nbsp;holds a&nbsp;black belt. In 1998, under the teachings of Greg Nelson, Mike began training in Brazilian Jiu Jitsu and received his blue belt in 1999 and his black belt in 2009.<\\/p>\"}},\"71\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"45\"],\"staffName\":\"Nathan Bagby\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 3rd degree black belt, Muay Thai \",\"body\":\"<p>Nathanael \\u201cNathan\\u201d Bagby is a 3rd degree black belt and an accomplished Muay Thai fighter and instructor. Nathan first became interested and started training in martial arts at the age of 8, and in the past 25 years, has trained in Isshinryu Karate, Eskrima, Tae Kwon Do, American Kickboxing, Brazilian Jiu Jitsu, Close Quarter Combat, Boxing, and Muay Thai. &nbsp;Nathan has successfully competed&nbsp;in several amateur and professional kickboxing and Muay Thai bouts.&nbsp;<\\/p>\"}},\"30\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"62\"],\"staffName\":\"Jayda Clayton\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 2nd degree black belt\",\"body\":\"<p>Jayda Clayton, a 3rd&nbsp;degree black belt, began her training in January 2007 at the ripe old age of 4. A prodigy of Master Steven Sosa, Jayda received her yellow and brown belts in 2007 and 2009, respectively. At age 7, Jayda became Master Sosa\\u2019s first and youngest student in the Tim Kirby lineage&nbsp;to receive her black belt. Jayda has competed in numerous local, state and national karate competitions and won over 60 trophies in sparring and kata competitions with over 40 of them being first place positions.<\\/p>\"}},\"66\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"48\"],\"staffName\":\"Johnny Rodriguez\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, Machado black belt\",\"body\":\"<p>Professor Johnny Rodriguez is a highly skilled black belt in Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu with over 20 years of training in several martial art forms including Kenpo karate, Aikido, Judo and Muay Thai. Professor Rodriguez teaches workshops, self-defense seminars, and has previously worked in law enforcement. &nbsp;Professor Rodriguez actively coaches students in preparation for Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu tournaments and MMA bouts and still competes in many Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu tournaments.&nbsp;<\\/p>\"}},\"67\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"49\"],\"staffName\":\"Gerardo Mulas\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, Certified Personal Trainer, Yoga\",\"body\":\"<p>Gerardo Mulas is a certified personal trainer, yoga and martial arts expert whose mission is educating students the benefits of fitness,&nbsp;health and wellness goals. Gerardo specializes in sports performance, weight loss, injury rehabilitation, stress relief, nutritional counseling and meal planning. Gerardo has over two decades of professional and collegiate athletics under his belt, along with extensive training in kickboxing, boxing and grappling.<\\/p>\"}},\"69\":{\"type\":\"staff\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"image\":[\"43\"],\"staffName\":\"Sovandy Om\",\"staffTitle\":\"Instructor, 5th degree black belt\",\"body\":\"<p>Master Sovandy Om is a 5th degree black belt, kickboxing fitness certified trainer and a FPMA student favorite. Master Om has trained extensively in Tae Kwon Do, MMA, Gymnastic, as well as Crossfit. Along with a passion for martial arts, Master Om has an even bigger passion for fitness. Master Om works tirelessly with helping the students execute proper technique to achieve the maximum benefits, as well as helping students reach and exceed their fitness goals.<\\/p>\"}}},\"81\":\"\",\"4\":\"\",\"3\":\"\"}}', '2016-09-22 18:58:53', '2016-09-22 18:58:53', '14a383b8-31cb-4f87-9520-dd266e31c4f0'),
