 ('1', '15', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Kick. Punch. Learn.', '<p>Freddie Poole’s Martial Arts® offers an exclusive hybrid training system that incorporates the traditional training values and principles of karate and tae-kwon-do with a contemporary system of combat, self-defense and fitness.</p>', '#000000', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-16 02:47:49', '2017-02-14 16:31:18', 'f2d76f37-eb8f-4832-ad82-f0c1890bec23'),
 ('2', '18', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Approach', '<p>The key to our success is each discipline being introduced in stages to our student, rather than a front-loading program. This methodical approach ensures students are learning and mastering techniques at the highest level, as opposed to just going through motions. Additionally, we have a variety of skilled instructors teaching our programs. This gives students an advantage of learning martial arts from varied perspectives, which enhances the quality of the training. Each instructor at FPMA® is trained to recognize a student’s personality, learning style, and individual needs.</p>', '#000000', '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-16 04:17:39', '2017-02-14 16:31:18', 'c1857473-ee8a-4f42-888d-7ef19a36f487'),
 ('3', '21', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'Dragons (4 – 6 YO)', '<p>Specifically designed for children four to six years of age where they will begin to learn the fundamental life skills such as self-discipline, focus, self-control respect, patience and confidence. Dragons will also learn fine motor skills such as strength, balance, flexibility, and coordination.</p>', '1', '#000000', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-24 02:37:17', '2016-10-12 03:29:11', '728f794f-be3e-4a00-8dba-a4629229b816'),
 ('4', '22', 'en_us', '', '<p>Our Dragons program has a fun and energetic class format helps the young students develop skills that set them up for success in life. The structure of the Freddie Poole Dragons program is a key principle of success of the student as it’s a preparatory training program for the Junior Martial Arts Program</p>', '#000000', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-24 02:37:17', '2016-10-12 03:29:11', 'ab12eaea-f6f0-4a14-86c0-83ab94274993'),
 ('6', '25', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'North Texas Martial Arts', '<p>North Texas Martial Arts is a certified partner school of Freddie Poole Martial Arts; we leverage the same martial arts curriculum as FPMA. North Texas Martial Art is led by Master Steve Sosa, a true martial artist with over 30 years of experience and multiple accolades, who has dedicated his passion for martial arts into teaching and coaching students.</p>', '1', '#000000', '17194 Preston Rd. #215  Dallas, TX United States 75248', 'North Texas Martial Arts', '<p><strong>LADIES&nbsp;SELF&nbsp;DEFENSE&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong>+&nbsp;KICKBOXING&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong class=\"redactor-inline-converted\">February 13th - March 23rd&nbsp;&nbsp;<br></strong></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p><strong class=\"redactor-inline-converted\">Mon. +&nbsp;Wed. at 8PM&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong class=\"redactor-inline-converted\">Tu. +Thur. at 10AM</strong></p><p><strong class=\"redactor-inline-converted\">Call for more details!&nbsp;</strong></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>17194 Preston Road, Suite 215<br>Dallas, Texas 75248<br><a href=\"http://tel:972.323.0027\">972.232.0027</a></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-24 04:22:43', '2017-02-17 23:29:41', '9c86a7f4-3bb5-4019-a21e-fdd9ea9c5935'),
 ('7', '28', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'Instructors', '<p>Our instructors have spent many years perfecting the martial arts craft and continue to go through extensive testing training and certifications to ensure that we are able to provide our students with the best care and instruction. </p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Here, we’re family, and we&nbsp;enjoy what we do and enjoy sharing that passion with others. Collectively we invest in each student, as we feel that their success is our success!</p>', '1', '#000000', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-25 02:46:04', '2017-02-07 20:13:19', '18868743-9283-401f-8b46-e1c8dd8d8d6e'),
 ('8', '29', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Steve Sosa', 'Instructor, 8th degree black belt', '<p>NTMA is operated by Master Steve Sosa, 8th degree black belt, winner of the “Golden Greek Award”- the highest award given by the Amateur Organization of Karate and is also a member of the Martial Arts Hall of Fame.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;He is a highly skilled martial artist with over 30 years’ experience and was&nbsp;trained by legendary martial artists such as Tim Kirby,&nbsp;Allen Steen, Ray McCallum, Billye Jackson, and Demetrius “The Greek” Havanas. In April 2011, Master Sosa was honored with the \"Positive Coaching Alliance’s Double-Goal Award”. It is bestowed upon to coaches who emphasize positive life skills, as well as work ethic and drive into their students’ training. Master Sosa is a very passionate trainer! Parents have given him much praise for his gentle, but firm style of explaining the mechanics of each technique and form, as well as implementing positive life skills to the younger students.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>In 2010 Master Sosa started North Texas Martial Arts (NTMA), which ultimately joined Freddie Poole Martial Arts in 2011.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-25 02:46:04', '2017-02-07 20:13:19', '7b3ca566-113b-46bb-b63c-81cbcbbe413d'),
 ('9', '30', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayda Clayton', 'Instructor, 3rd degree black belt', '<p>Jayda Clayton, a 3rd&nbsp;degree black belt, began her training in January 2007 at the ripe old age of 4. A prodigy of Master Steven Sosa, Jayda received her yellow and brown belts in 2007 and 2009, respectively. At age 7, Jayda became Master Sosa’s first and youngest student in the Tim Kirby lineage&nbsp;to receive her black belt. Jayda has competed in numerous local, state and national karate competitions and won over 60 trophies in sparring and kata competitions with over 40 of them being first place positions.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-25 02:46:04', '2017-02-07 20:13:20', 'a611b8da-107a-4bf5-b572-6da8081217ac'),
 ('10', '31', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Westin Poole', 'Instructor, 3rd degree black belt', '<p>Westin Poole’s love for karate kicked in as a kid when he&nbsp;began training in martial arts at the age of 6. By 2009, Westin was a certified 1st degree black belt and has no plans of slowing down. He has been teaching for almost eight years and enjoys working with children. The mission behind his teaching is inspiring his students to reach their goals and see the benefits of their hard work.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-25 02:46:04', '2017-02-07 20:13:19', '19a705af-1b19-4dea-9c5f-6a5d91f52f4d'),
 ('11', '35', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'Freddie Poole Martial Arts', '<p>Freddie Poole Martial Arts is conveniently located in Highland Park, just minutes away from Highland Park High School and McCulloch Intermediate School.&nbsp; We offer classes six days a week and have something for everyone in the family, check out our current class schedule below.</p>', '1', '#000000', '5757 W. Lovers Lane #217 Dallas, TX United States 75209', 'Freddie Poole\'s Martial Arts', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '<p>5757 West Lovers Lane, Suite 217<br>Dallas,&nbsp;TX United States 75209<br><a href=\"tel:2143525425\">214.352.5425</a></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-03-26 22:44:34', '2017-02-17 21:48:35', 'a726a04e-fe3a-4fa5-97c1-df5370879208'),
 ('12', '52', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Locations', '<p>We currently have 2 locations to serve you.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-04-21 04:20:31', '2017-02-14 16:31:18', 'ef05437f-c94a-445b-a453-fd71578d8c42'),
 ('13', '53', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '', '<p>Come see for yourself why our martial arts system has been so popular for so many years. Our black belt instructors are here to help you achieve all your marital art and fitness goals.</p>', '', 'col-3-of-5', 'col-2-of-5', '#000000', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '1', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-04-21 04:20:31', '2017-02-14 16:31:18', 'a8d4f829-a79c-42c6-9c4c-b2252076f435'),
 ('14', '54', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'FPMA – Special Events', '', 'dallas', '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-04-21 04:35:34', '2017-02-17 21:48:35', '8f0483e0-0b93-4bf7-bd57-6449b475cf00'),
 ('15', '55', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'Events', '<p>We pride ourselves in offering superior service and training for parents and kids. Outside of our extensive martial arts programs offered at both of our Dallas locations, FPMA offers various extra personal services that are very educational, affordable and definitely FUN! From private birthday celebrations to women’s self-defense classes, there’s something for everyone at&nbsp;FPMA.</p>', '1', '#000000', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-04-21 04:39:51', '2017-02-14 16:49:45', '0f3090f4-477e-4e9f-a79a-888e85755edb'),
 ('16', '56', 'en_us', 'Parent’s Nights Out', '<p>Got a date night or hang out with the crew night planned and need somewhere to take the kiddos? Bring ‘em to FPMA for Parents Night Out (PNO). The PNO program is on specified Saturdays from 5-9pm and welcomes both FPMA students and non-members to join in on a night full of pizza, movies, prizes and fun. <strong><em>Oh, did we mention Nerf gun wars, too?</em></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p> <a href=\"{entry:7:url}\">Just give one of our locations a call</a> for more information, pricing and dates for the next PNO.&nbsp;</p>', '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-04-21 04:39:51', '2017-02-14 16:49:45', 'f9271022-e637-4574-a114-76e03a7e9837'),
 ('17', '57', 'en_us', 'Birthday Parties', '<p>Celebrate the birthday for your little martial artists Freddie Poole style! FPMA offers a personal experience with one of our many skilled instructors, ready to teach all of the little partiers some exciting new martial arts moves and put a unique spin on a birthday celebrations. Decorations, music and food are welcome.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Interested in having your kid’s next birthday celebration at FPMA? <a href=\"tel:2143525425\">Give one of our locations a call</a> for more information.</p>', '#f5f5f5', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-04-21 04:39:51', '2017-02-14 16:49:45', '387f9b1e-6f67-4af5-aa9c-5ba558b6810a'),
 ('18', '58', 'en_us', 'Special Events', '<p><strong>FPMA is proud to announce our summer 2016 Karate Camp for kids.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Karate Camp is designed for children ages 4-11 and provides the perfect summer getaway for kids interested in learning more about the many forms of martial art. Give you kids the opportunity to learn more about boosting leadership and teamwork skills, building and improving self confidence, self defense techniques, bully awareness as well as fun martial arts games and drills. Choose from 2 summer camp sessions only a $25 deposit required to reserve a spot.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Reach out to a FPMA location for more details.</p>', '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-04-21 04:39:51', '2017-02-14 16:49:45', 'a68191cd-8473-4890-a850-69a3ea0148dc'),
 ('19', '59', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'Contact Us', '<p>Come see for yourself why our martial&nbsp;arts system has been popular for so many years. Our black belt instructors are here to help you achieve all your martial art and fitness goals.&nbsp;</p>', '0', '#000000', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-04-21 04:41:43', '2016-07-27 04:02:52', 'a838bf2b-23cf-4599-b2de-1cf451e202f6'),
 ('20', '60', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Contact Us', '', '#f5f5f5', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-04-21 04:42:25', '2016-07-27 04:02:52', '166aa9ec-ae2b-4c92-95f2-41f15e1c0b12'),
 ('21', '65', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Vanny Boon', 'Instructor, 5th degree black belt, Saekson Muay Thai ', '<p>Master Vanny Boon is a certified 5th degree black belt skilled in various forms of martial arts including Taekwondo Do, Muay Thai, Brazilian Jiu jitsu and Boxing. Master Boon’s passion and experience for martial arts began when he started training at the age of 5 and spans over 25 years.&nbsp;Master Boon trained under Grand Master Hong, Master Freddie Poole and Muay Thai world champion Saekson Janjira.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-06 22:03:30', '2017-02-07 20:13:19', 'aee3c1c5-d0a4-46cc-8269-d6b1524ca76f'),
 ('22', '66', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Johnny Rodriguez', 'Instructor, Machado black belt', '<p>Professor Johnny Rodriguez is a highly skilled black belt in Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu with over 20 years of training in several martial art forms including Kenpo karate, Aikido, Judo and Muay Thai. Professor Rodriguez teaches workshops, self-defense seminars, and has previously worked in law enforcement. &nbsp;Professor Rodriguez actively coaches students in preparation for Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu tournaments and MMA bouts and still competes in many Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu tournaments.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-06 22:03:30', '2017-02-07 20:13:20', '371f7237-b3b1-4bef-87d1-a60cf1204569'),
 ('23', '67', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Gerardo Mulas', 'Instructor, Certified Personal Trainer, Yoga', '<p>Gerardo Mulas is a certified personal trainer, yoga and martial arts expert whose mission is educating students the benefits of fitness,&nbsp;health and wellness goals. Gerardo specializes in sports performance, weight loss, injury rehabilitation, stress relief, nutritional counseling and meal planning. Gerardo has over two decades of professional and collegiate athletics under his belt, along with extensive training in kickboxing, boxing and grappling.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-06 22:03:30', '2017-02-07 20:13:20', '4c1cb86b-5817-448e-9715-56e6f9852b0d'),
 ('24', '68', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Randy Stem', 'Instructor, 5th degree black belt, fitness trainer ', '<p>Randy Stem is a 5th degree black belt trained in Karate, Kickboxing, and Judo and Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu. Randy studied under the teachings of Allen Steen, widely recognized as the \'Father of American Taekwondo\', and has over 45 years of experience mastering martial arts. Randy strongly encourages his students to build a firm foundation in martial arts early on by focusing on the development of basic fundamental motor skills and concepts.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-06 22:03:30', '2017-02-07 20:13:19', 'a5332076-fb63-4c26-8662-59309a194ac1'),
 ('25', '69', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Sovandy Om', 'Instructor, 5th degree black belt', '<p>Master Sovandy Om is a 5th degree black belt, kickboxing fitness certified trainer and a FPMA student favorite. Master Om has trained extensively in Tae Kwon Do, MMA, Gymnastic, as well as Crossfit. Along with a passion for martial arts, Master Om has an even bigger passion for fitness. Master Om works tirelessly with helping the students execute proper technique to achieve the maximum benefits, as well as helping students reach and exceed their fitness goals.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-06 22:03:30', '2017-02-07 20:13:20', 'ed8d68ad-e98f-4361-a7df-35b514642d2f'),
 ('26', '70', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Alex Garcia', 'Instructor, 2nd degree black belt', '<p>Alex Garcia is a 2nd degree black belt in Tae Kwon Do who gravitated towards the world of martial arts at the age of 4. Alex soon began training to develop and perfect his skills for martial arts and became a student at Freddie Poole\'s Martial Arts at the age of 10. Within 2 years, Alex’s dedication transformed him into an avid competitor.&nbsp;Alex received several 1st place wins in state martial arts championships.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-06 22:03:30', '2017-02-07 20:13:20', '1ab1e2a5-a599-4b21-9367-e5f417237c8c'),
 ('27', '71', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Nathan Bagby', 'Instructor, 3rd degree black belt, Muay Thai ', '<p>Nathanael “Nathan” Bagby is a 3rd degree black belt and an accomplished Muay Thai fighter and instructor. Nathan first became interested and started training in martial arts at the age of 8, and in the past 25 years, has trained in Isshinryu Karate, Eskrima, Tae Kwon Do, American Kickboxing, Brazilian Jiu Jitsu, Close Quarter Combat, Boxing, and Muay Thai. &nbsp;Nathan has successfully competed&nbsp;in several amateur and professional kickboxing and Muay Thai bouts.&nbsp;</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-06 22:03:30', '2017-02-07 20:13:20', '73dc49b7-91d4-4d1e-befe-8d9b8bc3357f'),
 ('28', '72', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Mike Rose', 'Instructor, Machado black belt ', '<p>Mike Rose has over 25 years of martial arts training, competition, and teaching experience in both Judo and Brazilian Jiu Jitsu. Mike started training in Judo in 1992 and currently&nbsp;holds a&nbsp;black belt. In 1998, under the teachings of Greg Nelson, Mike began training in Brazilian Jiu Jitsu and received his blue belt in 1999 and his black belt in 2009.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-06 22:03:30', '2017-02-07 20:13:20', '28cd70ca-e779-45c6-9712-506d481676da'),
 ('29', '75', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'About Freddie', '<p>Freddie Poole began martial arts training in 1981, at the age of seven years old. He began studying at Southwest Karate Academy under Demetrius “Golden Greek” Havanas. Southwest Karate Academy produced some of the best martial arts champions and competitors in the world, at that time. The 80’s were the tail end of the “Texas Blood and Guts” era of martial arts. The lineage began with Jhoon Rhee and his first black belt was Allen Steen. Steen went on to train many black belts and students and Texas was known for producing some of the best fighters in the country. Tim Kirby, Billye Jackson, Raymond McCallum, and Santae Wilson Jr.&nbsp; were some of the world-class competitors who had influence over Poole’s training and development.</p>', '1', '#000000', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-15 02:59:06', '2016-09-27 14:34:29', 'd67fadfa-13c1-4d98-afad-25844248a68e'),
 ('30', '76', 'en_us', '', '<h3>Poole received his 1st degree black belt in 1986, under Tim Kirby, Billye Jackson and Raymond McCallum. Poole competed in the AOK and was a top ranked competitor in forms and fighting for many years as a junior competitor.</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Poole began working for and training with long time friend and kickboxing/MMA champion Guy Mezger in 1993. Poole began honing his boxing and kickboxing skills with Mezger, Billye Jackson, Santae Wilson Jr. and Coach Charles Brown and went on to win a national title in 1997, which earned a spot on the US National Kickboxing team.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Poole’s boxing experience comes from training with some of the best coaches in the business. Phil Sawyer and Olympic Boxing Bronze medalist Charles Brown have influenced Poole in his boxing training, as well as Alex Andrade, David Douglas and Michael Montoya.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Poole has several years of Muay Thai experience, training with Francisco Sanchez of New World Combat, as well as World Muay Thai champion and MMA veteran Pete Spratt and Muay Thai champion Jason House.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Poole’s Judo experience comes from training with Master Vince Tamura and Judo Black Belt Rico Castro.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Poole currently trains under the tutelage of 8th degree Brazilian Jiu Jitsu master, Carlos Machado, where he holds a brown belt and is a proud affiliate of Machado Jiu Jitsu. Poole has also trained with many talented Brazilian Jiu Jitsu black belts including Kenny McClure, Jeff Sawyer, Rico Castro and Taryn Douglas.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Poole has competed all over the United States and internationally in Europe, winning a KICK International title in 2004 along with many team karate titles from 1999-2004. Poole also fought for Team Texas in Chuck Norris’s televised fight league, The World Combat League.</p><p>Poole has performed and worked alongside some of the top names in the action world including Sylvester Stallone, Chuck Norris, Ben Affleck, Jason Statham and many others. Poole can be seen on popular television shows like The Walking Dead, Sons of Anarchy, From Dusk till Dawn and Marvel’s AGENTS of S.H.I.E.L.D, to name a few. &nbsp;He has also served as a stunt double, performing various feats of action for actors Sylvester Stallone, Frank Grillo, Jesse Metcalfe as well as many others. As a fight coordinator and stunt coordinator, Poole oversees and is in charge of action for <a href=\"http://www.imdb.com/name/nm1336664/\">feature films</a> that can be seen anywhere from Netflix to the big screen and network TV shows!</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n', '#000000', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-15 02:59:06', '2016-09-27 14:34:29', '0cf706ae-759a-4cc0-b789-661f2ee970c9'),
 ('31', '77', 'en_us', 'Women’s Self Defense Seminars', '<p>Safety for our members is a major priority for us. FPMA offers self-defense classes for women to learn how to protect themselves and their loved ones from unexpected attacks. Join FPMA for one of our Women’s Self Defense Seminars in partnership with Not Dead Yet Apparel. Come get hands-on training as we demonstrate various self-defense techniques, learn empowering safety awareness and practices. Attendance is always free, but we accept donations of $25 or more to benefit a designated local non-profit organization. Take the first step by contacting one of our locations for more information.</p>', '#f5f5f5', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-15 03:07:18', '2017-02-14 16:49:45', 'df398b75-66b1-4dec-84d4-cd11760c52b0'),
 ('32', '78', 'en_us', 'Personal Training ', '<p>For the member who wants to learn the valuable techniques of martial arts outside of a group setting, FPMA offers specialized one-on-one training sessions. Members get individually structured personal instruction from one of our certified martial arts trainers. Training sessions are customized to benefit each student in any skill level, from a novice student wanting a more personal experience or an advanced student preparing for competition.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"{entry:32:url}\">Contact one of our two Dallas locations</a> for more details.&nbsp;</p>', '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-15 03:07:18', '2017-02-14 16:49:45', '670bac2c-9d6d-4d3f-8643-a51b3d5a6461'),
 ('33', '79', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'Juniors', '<p><strong>Juniors: (7 to 12 years old)&nbsp;<br></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Freddie Poole’s Martial Arts®&nbsp;junior martial arts program&nbsp;is a unique training system that combines traditional values and principles with a modern system of combat, self-defense and fitness. Our exclusive system and program is a hybrid style, which incorporates training methods of karate and tae-kwon-do with westernized boxing, judo and Brazilian Jiu Jitsu. FPMA has a variety of instructors teaching our program. This gives students an advantage of learning martial arts from different perspectives, which enhances the quality of training.&nbsp;</p>', '1', '#000000', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-15 03:14:24', '2016-10-12 03:29:00', 'f21fe7a0-789b-4c40-9795-4caa5e401f46'),
 ('34', '80', 'en_us', '', '<p>Our Juniors program focuses on advancement and growth based on each child’s individual pace. The key to our success is each discipline is introduced in stages to the student, rather than front-loading a program. Juniors will begin to grasp the concept of self-discipline as they achieve goals. When he/she tackles more difficult goals, the self-confidence grows and serves as a strong foundation in all aspects of life.</p>', '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-15 03:14:24', '2016-10-12 03:29:00', '417a7782-fdf0-4fc0-acbe-6616ae5bff18'),
 ('35', '82', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu', '<p><strong>Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu: (7 to 12-year-old + Adults)&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The sport of Brazilian Jiu Jitsu can be quite complex. Our intro program helps break down all the essential concepts of the sport making it much easier to pick up for anybody. Freddie Poole’s Martial arts is a proud affiliate of the Carlos Machado BJJ association and network. Carlos Machado is nephew to one of the founders of Brazilian Jiu Jitsu, late master Carlos Gracie. Carlos is determined to keep the legacy going through teaching and partnering with others including our very own, Freddie Poole.&nbsp;</p>', '1', '#000000', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-15 03:20:08', '2016-10-12 03:30:16', '67b0a58e-269a-4af5-8147-93435505c906'),
 ('36', '83', 'en_us', '', '<p>Our classes are curriculum oriented, providing a fast paced yet easy approach to learning Brazilian Jiu Jitsu for children (7-12 years of age) and adults. Students achieve great results in a short amount of time learning realistic skills great for both self-defense and increasing fitness and stamina. Students also learn strategies for advancing in rank after completing time and skill requirements, all in a fun and safe environment.</p>', '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-15 03:20:08', '2016-10-12 03:30:16', 'b5533ea2-b512-4631-9d88-a84b74ac7e3a'),
 ('37', '84', 'en_us', 'Kids BJJ Program', '<p>The FPMA Brazilian Jiu Jitsu kids program is the perfect tool to change your child’s life forever. Lessons learned both on and off the mat will instill in them a confidence and self-belief that will continue with them throughout their lives. Plus, it’s FUN! FPMA stands firm on our anti-bullying policies, which have been reverse engineered to safely and effectively repel any aggressor, with truly phenomenal results.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Overall, the Kids BBJ program is designed to develop a sense of discipline, determination, leadership, commitment, responsibility, good sportsmanship and confidence into our future leaders</p>', '#f5f5f5', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-15 03:20:08', '2016-10-12 03:30:16', '5941b1fd-eb72-48d8-87e3-b0d55fb19eda'),
 ('38', '85', 'en_us', 'Adults BJJ Fundamentals', '<p>FPMA BJJ Fundamentals Program is designed to teach the overall self-defense strategy of Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu. The class begins with a pre-workout involving many body weight exercises and it will teach you the basics, from learning how to fall, to clinching, taking down and successfully setting up and applying a submission hold as well as various escapes. We provide a detailed instruction in wrestling, judo, and Brazilian Jiu Jitsu, as they are all relevant to mastership. The class ends with positional training that helps students focus on the lesson of the week and get a feel for live training. Through repetition techniques, your training will slowly prepare you to begin drilling at a full resistance.</p>', '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-15 03:20:08', '2016-10-12 03:30:16', '0f7621d5-967d-4787-a968-03232f518fb6'),
 ('40', '88', 'en_us', '', '<p>As intimidating as it may sound, kickboxing is perfect for all ladies. From beginners to experts, you’re sure to get the most from the&nbsp;private like atmosphere and pace of the class. With a dedicated staff of skilled professionals, kickboxing is the ideal workout option for mothers looking for an alternative to going to the gym and unique workout options with morning, afternoon and evening classes available.</p>', '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-15 03:22:24', '2016-10-12 03:30:44', 'f49de6df-c1ba-45b6-9f42-ad1b496e9ef1'),
 ('41', '90', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'Martial Arts', '<p><strong>Martial Arts (7 to 12 years old + Adults)</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Martial arts training helps to develop an indomitable spirit in practitioners of any age and any skill level. FPMA martial arts program focuses on increased concentration, ability to memorize and awareness. Many of our students say there is no better stress relief than coming onto the mat and pushing their minds, bodies and spirits to the limits.</p>', '1', '#000000', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-15 03:26:32', '2016-08-04 06:11:21', '73d5fee4-7090-492f-a483-b68d71a17f03'),
 ('42', '91', 'en_us', 'Martial Arts: Juniors', '<h3>Freddie Poole Beginner’s Course (White Belts):</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>This class begins with traditional Chung Do Kwon (Tae Kwon Do) and karate. Students learn basic commands, basic stances and blocks, and basic kicks and punches. This program implements boxing to enhance and modernize the system. Students’ progress through short-term goals (stripes) to reach their long-term goal (colored rank). Students learn practical and situational self-defense as well. Classes are thirty minutes (for greater retention of material), in a fun, yet disciplined and true martial arts environment.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>Freddie Poole Intermediate Course (Orange through Purple belts):</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>The Freddie Poole Intermediate Karate Course focuses on the student’s concentration and increases physical fitness through agility and coordination drills. Balance and kicking technique are emphasized as well as an introduction to sparring technique and strategy. Each step of the way, children are guided towards a true understanding of their new found skills and associated responsibilities. To balance and complete the intermediate program, students will learn basic judo and take downs (blue belt). Class time will increase to 45 minutes to an hour long.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3>Freddie Poole Advanced Course (Red through Black Belt):</h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>In the Freddie Poole Advanced Karate Program, students are introduced to advanced technique drills and advanced forms. Students’ progress to a more intense and advanced sparring level in preparation for Black Belt. To create a well-balanced program and student, the Freddie Poole Advanced course focuses on self-defense and mental awareness, with a heavy emphasis on grappling and Brazilian Jiu Jitsu fitness goals.</p>', '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-15 03:26:32', '2016-08-04 06:11:21', '669b8866-1d90-4755-9832-e5e477eb5179'),
 ('43', '92', 'en_us', 'Martial Arts: Adults', '<p>The adult curriculum is a structured traditional program complimented by modern training techniques that provide students the opportunity to understand theory as well as practical application.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Students learn techniques and strategies that can truly be life-saving skills as well as give overall fitness. New students will see improvement in their coordination, flexibility and muscle tone in just a few short weeks. Those who become proficient in martial arts will have better stamina, strength and peace of mind that comes from knowing they can efficiently and effectively defend themselves.</p>', '#f5f5f5', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-15 03:26:32', '2016-08-04 06:11:21', '431fc126-c2dd-46ee-9286-fedc5f658452'),
 ('44', '94', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'Muay Thai Kickboxing', '<p><strong>Muay Thai: Adults</strong><br></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Muay Thai is a combat sport from Thailand that uses stand-up strikes along with various clinch techniques. This physical and mental discipline is known as \"the art of eight limbs\" because it is characterized by the combined use of fists, elbows, knees and shins during training.&nbsp;</p>', '1', '#000000', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-15 03:30:34', '2016-08-11 17:50:13', 'b96c5949-c985-4418-9157-d7bf2a05347c'),
 ('45', '95', 'en_us', '', '<p>Individuals participating in this program achieve outstanding physical conditioning due to the highly intense yet fun&nbsp;nature of striking through the use of bag&nbsp;drills, mitt drills&nbsp;and pad work. This self paced class is taught by high level instructors with years of training in this discipline, who encourage each participant to reach their full physical potential. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>', '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-15 03:30:34', '2016-08-11 17:50:13', 'f74ab22b-f9db-41f6-818e-870065515ad0'),
 ('46', '97', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'Leadership', '<p>The FPMA Leadership Program is an instructor recommended program. Students must first attain a blue belt through the Intermediate Program. They must also demonstrate leadership qualities to receive nominations.</p>', '1', '#000000', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-15 03:31:34', '2016-08-11 17:49:49', 'cd24b83b-9bbd-429b-ab02-6d8e0555c449'),
 ('47', '98', 'en_us', '', '<p>The FPMA Leadership Program focuses on developing leaders, not only in Martial Arts, but in the community as well. Each month leadership students are required to demonstrate and apply a new leadership skill at home, at school, and in the Martial&nbsp;Arts training.</p>', '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-15 03:31:34', '2016-08-11 17:49:49', 'b6e0ffcb-cc1d-42c8-aab6-6585bf19df49'),
 ('48', '103', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'NTMA – Special Events', '', 'northDallas', '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '#000000', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-15 04:00:58', '2017-02-17 23:29:41', '182b8ee5-2343-4d83-9425-d691cd4533c1'),
 ('49', '112', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'Ladies Kickboxing', '<p>The Ladies Kickboxing program is exclusively for ladies looking to combine an intense physical workout with the added perk of self-defense practices. Outside of incorporating various types of kickboxing techniques and strikes, FPMA Ladies kickboxing helps to educate students on many aspects of weight training, physical conditioning and yoga.&nbsp;</p>', '1', '#000000', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-06-27 01:38:17', '2016-10-12 03:30:44', 'e2990b67-a75d-45e4-8d74-67f7729fefd9'),
 ('50', '129', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'FPMA', '<p>Since opening its doors in 2004, Freddie Poole\'s Martial Arts has been impacting thousands of lives in the community. Our friendly staff looks forward each day to helping our students achieve their goals.<br></p>', '1', '#000000', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-07-14 02:32:44', '2016-08-01 03:13:07', '14afdfea-cbff-4f77-92cf-b0e0fbe3df2a'),
 ('51', '132', 'en_us', '', '<p>Although standards are set high, each student at FPMA is evaluated on an individual basis to ensure progression on their own timeline. This approach ensures students achieve and&nbsp;earn rank on their own merit.&nbsp;We encourage our students to trust the process and enjoy it. Earning a black belt at FPMA is a once in a lifetime experience! The dedicated team of instructors at FPMA have taken their experience of martial arts and created a well-rounded training system for all ages. Freddie Poole’s Martial Arts is the most balanced martial arts training system, combining traditional training elements with practical real world application. By integrating both of these elements into one system, one can truly train in mixed martial arts.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Freddie Poole\'s Martial Arts has a <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/FreddiePMA\">YouTube</a> channel for students looking to have a better understanding of techniques taught in classes or for those just looking to brush up on their skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/FreddiePMA\"></a></p>', '#000000', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-07-14 02:57:12', '2016-08-01 03:13:07', '24a227ad-0e8c-45ff-a275-4c45e10a67bf'),
