 ('56', '277', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'Resources ', '<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLQd35_25XfTyVMOA36GCe9q51m-Rm5plO\" target=\"_blank\"></a>Freddie Poole\'s Martial Arts has a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/FreddiePMA\"></a><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/FreddiePMA/videos\">YouTube</a>&nbsp;channel for students looking to have a better understanding of techniques taught in classes or for those just looking to brush up on their skills.</p>', '1', '#000000', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-09-12 07:56:46', '2016-09-19 03:59:13', '7138be7d-b2a6-44fd-89a2-854acf023cba'),
 ('57', '282', 'en_us', 'Ladies Self Defense + Kickboxing ', '<p>This six-week class&nbsp;is exclusively for ladies looking to combine an intense physical workout with the added perk of self-defense practices. In addition to&nbsp;incorporating various types of kickboxing techniques and strikes,&nbsp;this program aims&nbsp;to educate women on many aspects of weight training, physical conditioning and yoga.&nbsp;</p><p>Classes offered at <strong>North Texas Martial Arts</strong> from&nbsp;February 13th - March 23rd:&nbsp;</p><p>Monday +&nbsp;Wednesday at 8pm&nbsp;<br>Tuesday + Thursday at 10am&nbsp;</p><p>Space is limited. Call 972.232.0027&nbsp;today to sign up!&nbsp;</p>', '#ffffff', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-09-15 15:06:57', '2017-02-14 16:49:45', '086f9c23-c3b4-4cab-b484-572531282409'),
 ('58', '294', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'Specials', '<p>We’re excited to bring you&nbsp;new offers&nbsp;on a regular basis. See below to check out&nbsp;our current specials!</p>', '1', '#000000', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-09-17 20:22:34', '2016-12-02 16:05:13', '6b3db959-23c8-4d6f-933d-2e5ef10bb1b4'),
 ('59', '295', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Current Specials', '', '2016-09-17 20:22:34', '2016-12-02 16:05:13', 'c1d8e43c-d8a4-44d4-bcf2-54f7dd24bfb3'),
 ('60', '346', 'en_us', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', 'NTMA', '<p>North Texas Martial Arts is a certified partner school of Freddie Poole Martial Arts; we leverage the same martial &nbsp;arts curriculum as FPMA. North Texas Martial Arts is led by Master Steve Sosa, a true martial artist with over 30 years of experience and multiple accolades, who has dedicated his passion for martial arts into teaching and coaching students.</p>', '1', '#000000', '', '', '', NULL, NULL, NULL, '', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-13 21:13:50', '2017-01-24 16:05:51', 'd64a5648-7c4c-4f1f-aca9-51126d99595c'),
 ('61', '347', 'en_us', '', '<p>NTMA offers group and individual classes for all ages and abilities in the art of Karate, Tae Kwon Do, Boxing and Self-defense, as well as Private Lessons and Personal Training.&nbsp;<br></p><p>Although standards are set high, each student at NTMA&nbsp;is evaluated on an individual basis to ensure progression on their own timeline. This approach ensures students achieve and&nbsp;earn rank on their own merit.&nbsp;We encourage our students to trust the process and enjoy it. Earning a black belt at NTMA is a once in a lifetime experience! The dedicated team of instructors at NTMA have taken their experience of martial arts and created a well-rounded training system for all ages. North Texas Martial Arts&nbsp;is the most balanced martial arts training system, combining traditional training elements with practical real world application. By integrating both of these elements into one system, one can truly train in mixed martial arts.</p><p><br>North Texas&nbsp;Martial Arts has a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/user/FreddiePMA\">YouTube</a>&nbsp;channel for students looking to have a better understanding of techniques taught in classes or for those just looking to brush up on their skills</p>', '#000000', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '0', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2016-10-13 21:13:50', '2017-01-24 16:05:51', '4fd8a42a-fea6-4cbf-a701-f4bee3e1671c');
